ActImmigration and Refugee Protection Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Immigration and Refugee Protection Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the IMMIGRATION AND REFUGEE PROTECTION REGULATIONS in order to 1) strenghten Canada's immigration program and protect the safety and security of Canadians; and 2) enhance the integrity and security of the temporary resident program through the use of BIOMETRICS (fingerprints and digital photographs).
